<h2 id="致谢">致谢</h2>

<p>托管于<a href="https://pages.github.com/">Github Pages</a>，感谢。</p>

<p>博客引擎来自于<a href="https://github.com/jekyll/jekyll">jekyll/jekyll</a>，感谢。</p>

<p>CDN加速服务来自于<a href="https://www.jsdelivr.com/">jsdelivr</a>，感谢。</p>

<p>博客主题基于<a href="https://github.com/poole/lanyon">poole/lanyon</a>，感谢。</p>

<p>图标库来自于<a href="https://fontawesome.com/"><i class="fab fa-font-awesome"></i>fontawesome-free</a>，感谢。</p>

<p>留言和阅读量系统来自于<a href="https://valine.js.org/">Valine</a>和<a href="https://leancloud.cn/">LeanCloud</a>，感谢。</p>

<p>页面统计来自于<a href="http://busuanzi.ibruce.info/">不蒜子</a>，感谢。</p>

<p>博文目录插件来自于<a href="https://github.com/ghiculescu/jekyll-table-of-contents">ghiculescu/jekyll-table-of-contents</a>，感谢。</p>

<p>博客搜索插件来自于<a href="https://github.com/christian-fei/Simple-Jekyll-Search">christian-fei/Simple-Jekyll-Search</a>，感谢。</p>

<p>代码高亮及插件来自于<a href="https://prismjs.com/">PrismJS</a>，感谢。</p>

<p>Live2D来自于<a href="https://github.com/stevenjoezhang/live2d-widget">stevenjoezhang/live2d-widget</a>，感谢。</p>

<p>头像翻转效果来自于<a href="https://github.com/leopardpan/leopardpan.github.io">leopardpan/leopardpan.github.io</a>，感谢。</p>

